        "mainbody": "'''Zarkursk''' was the evil old [[black dragon]] who was an enemy of the [[dwarves]] of [[Clan Stonehand]] sometime before [[1372 DR]].",
        "History": "Zarkursk laired within a swamp in close vicinity to Clan Stonehand's mine. Given their close proximity, the dragon and the dwarves developed a bitter rivalry that culminated in Clan Stonehand's young warriors planning and executing a fateful attack on Zarkursk. They successfully slew the beast and inherited the sizable hoard that consisted mostly out of precious [[gem]]s."
